data.description: Step inside and be greeted by the timeless elegance of hardwood floors that flow seamlessly throughout, creating a sense of unity and sophistication. The open floor plan effortlessly connects each space, allowing for effortless entertaining and comfortable living. With four spacious bedrooms and two luxurious baths, there is ample room for family and guests to find their own sanctuary within this haven of style. Indulge in the luxury of a walk-in closet, providing an abundance of storage space while adding a touch of opulence to your daily routine. The two-car garage offers convenience and security, ensuring your vehicles are protected from the elements. Prepare culinary delights in the gourmet kitchen adorned with a generous island that not only serves as a focal point but also provides plenty of counter space for all your cooking endeavors. Every corner has been thoughtfully designed to maximize functionality without compromising on style. Nestled within a great neighborhood, this property offers more than just architectural allure; it promises an idyllic lifestyle where community thrives. Retreat to the expansive backyard oasis where memories will be made under the sheltering embrace of a covered patio.  Don't miss out on this captivating gem that combines modern luxury with everyday comfort. Your dream home awaits!  ****Seller to pay $10,000 in buyer's closing cost****
